text: Yisakale allaha arau te'omra raachulara biraud'dhe yud'dha karae arau prthiraita dhbansatmaka kama karai phurae sihamtara sasti kerala e'itorae'i ye, sihamtaka hatya karaa ha’ba athaba krauchabid'dha karaa ha’ba na'iba biparaita disara paraa hata bharai kati peloraa ha’ba ba sihamtaka desara paraa nirbasita karaa ha’ba. Prthiraita e'itorae'i sihamtara lanchana arau akhiraatata sihamtara babe ache maha sasti
